# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s26c_adb26ed9:

    # "I vaguely know where the casino Mariah mentioned is located. We passed it earlier today, but I didn’t pay much attention to it."
    "Tengo una vaga idea de dónde está el casino que mencionó Mariah. Pasamos por ahí hoy temprano, pero no le presté mucha atención."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s26c_6ce39ccf:

    # "As we load out of the RV, Marina’s dragging her feet."
    "Mientras bajamos del RV, Marina arrastra los pies."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s26c_22cd53c8:

    # Amber "Do you wanna wait here? I can just go take care of this and then come back."
    Amber "Хочешь остаться здесь? Я могу сама со всем разобраться и потом вернусь обратно."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s26c_517d713e:

    # Marina "No way!"
    Marina "Ну уж нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8924a59b:

    # Marina "I don’t wanna split up again."
    Marina "Я не хочу снова разделяться."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ba6999c1:

    # "After I lock up, I take her hand. Since I’m in the lead this time, the walk isn’t as slow."
    "Después de cerrar con llave, tomo su mano. Como esta vez yo voy al frente, la caminata no es tan lenta."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s26c_2735a7dd:

    # "With the evening approaching, the temperature’s gone down. At the same time, traffic is starting to build up."
    "Con la llegada de la tarde, la temperatura ha bajado. Al mismo tiempo, el tráfico empieza a aumentar."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s26c_b4699209:

    # "In a few hours, it’ll look like an entirely different city here. Once all the lights come on."
    "En unas horas, esto parecerá una ciudad completamente diferente. Una vez que se enciendan todas las luces."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s26c_9b1c21dc:

    # "The view of a big city at night, far in the distance, has always been one of my favorite sights."
    "La vista de una gran ciudad de noche, a lo lejos, siempre ha sido una de mis imágenes favoritas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s26c_13a727ed:

    # "I can remember staying up late when Gramps and I were on the road so that I could press like a sticker against the window and look."
    "Recuerdo quedarme despierto hasta tarde cuando el Abuelo y yo estábamos en la carretera, para poder pegarme a la ventana como una calcomanía y mirar."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s26c_3171949e:

    # "They sell postcards of New York and Atlanta and other places all lit up, because it’s so pretty."
    "Venden postales de Nueva York y Atlanta y otros lugares iluminados, porque es tan bonito."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s26c_085ee193:

    # "We’ve got a couple hours until then."
    "Nos quedan un par de horas hasta entonces."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s26c_83ac891d:

    # "Neither Marina nor I say much while we walk. Even given the situation, it doesn’t feel as awkward as some of our quiet times before."
    "Ni Marina ni yo decimos mucho mientras caminamos. Incluso dada la situación, no se siente tan incómodo como algunos de nuestros silencios anteriores."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ed68697a:

    # "Soon, we reach the building Mariah described."
    "Pronto llegamos al edificio que describió Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s26c_19281899:

    # Amber "This the place?"
    Amber "Это оно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s26c_9efc706e:

    # Marina "Yeah, this is it."
    Marina "Да, это оно."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s26c_5a7a4b82:

    # "We step inside."
    "Entramos."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s26c_fb9663bb:

    # "I can see why Mariah said this place might be closed soon. Although it’s pretty clean looking, there’s hardly anyone here."
    "Puedo ver por qué Mariah dijo que este lugar podría cerrar pronto. Aunque se ve bastante limpio, casi no hay nadie aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s26c_06484635:

    # "A couple of people occupy slot machines, far away from each other. Aside from those two, and a bored looking host, the place is pretty empty."
    "Un par de personas ocupan máquinas tragamonedas, lejos una de la otra. Aparte de esos dos, y un anfitrión con aspecto aburrido, el lugar está bastante vacío."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s26c_f3e37be7:

    # "Well, those three and the Trio. Mariah and her posse are seated on a semicircular couch. It and an identical couch form a circle around a card table."
    "Bueno, esos tres y el Trío. Mariah y su grupo están sentados en un sofá semicircular. Ese y otro sofá idéntico forman un círculo alrededor de una mesa de cartas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d12f4998:

    # "No greetings are exchanged as Marina and I take our places across from them."
    "No se intercambian saludos mientras Marina y yo tomamos nuestros lugares frente a ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s26c_10dcf5d0:

    # "A sealed deck of cards sits on the table. It’s got gaudy Las Vegas landmarks and logos all over it, but at least it’s legit."
    "Una baraja de cartas sellada está sobre la mesa. Tiene llamativos monumentos y logotipos de Las Vegas por todas partes, pero al menos es legítima."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s26c_dcc0f05d:

    # Amber "Should we ask that guy to come deal for us?"
    Amber "Мы должны попросить этого парня раздать нам?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c93c18be:

    # Mariah "Hell no. The only reason they don’t check ID is because they don’t care."
    Mariah "Нихрена. Они сейчас не спрашивают документы, только потому что им наплевать на это."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s26c_58e471c7:

    # Mariah "If you attract any attention they’ll throw you out."
    Mariah "Если привлечешь любое внимание — они вас вышвырнут."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c7617a7d:

    # Amber "Okay, so who will?"
    Amber "Ладно, тогда кто?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s26c_00b236f0:

    # Mariah "Tess can."
    Mariah "Тесс может."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s26c_812f3d76:

    # "Tess nods."
    "Tess asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s26c_942becd1:

    # Amber "Really?"
    Amber "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s26c_85c85a57:

    # Amber "No offense, but does she even know how?"
    Amber "Без обид, но она хоть знает как?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s26c_524d7c61:

    # Mariah "Of course she knows how, she’s not an idiot."
    Mariah "Конечно она знает, она не идиотка."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a270b67a:

    # Mariah "And before you get any ideas, she’s more likely to help you cheat than to help me."
    Mariah "И пока ты там себе не напридумывала, она скорее поможет сжульничать тебе, чем мне."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s26c_1ba00630:

    # "Tess nods again."
    "Tess asiente de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a3bfbe4d:

    # Tess "Just ask."
    Tess "Только попроси."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s26c_82367fbc:

    # Amber "Alright. That works for me."
    Amber "Ладушки. Меня устраивает."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s26c_72785046:

    # "Because if two underage girls are going to play, then why not have a ten year old deal the cards?"
    "Porque si dos chicas menores de edad van a jugar, ¿por qué no dejar que una niña de diez años reparta las cartas?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a417f672:

    # "Mariah slits open the plastic wrap on the deck and then hands it to Tess. The little girl takes out the instructional cards and the jokers and then shuffles."
    "Mariah abre el envoltorio de plástico de la baraja y luego se la entrega a Tess. La niña saca las cartas de instrucciones y los comodines, y luego baraja."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c087a476:

    # "I have to say, I’m impressed. She creates a bridge with the cards that’s way tidier than I could ever do."
    "Debo decir que estoy impresionado. Hace un puente con las cartas mucho más ordenado de lo que yo podría hacer jamás."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c05c90be:

    # "Mechanical, even."
    "Mecánico, incluso."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s26c_06e614a5:

    # Amber "So there are sixteen pieces total. We’ll go piece by piece, I guess?"
    Amber "Значит, всего шестнадцать частей. Играем кусочек за кусочком, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s26c_64b5c03c:

    # Mariah "Sure."
    Mariah "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s26c_9678a9e9:

    # "That means that I’d have to win eight hands in a row, without Mariah or the dealer winning any, to earn back all of Marina’s treasure. And I won’t settle for anything less than the full amount."
    "Eso significa que tendría que ganar ocho manos seguidas, sin que Mariah o la crupier ganen ninguna, para recuperar todo el tesoro de Marina. Y no me conformaré con menos que la cantidad completa."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e7523a48:

    # "We have a small stack of tokens near us that each represent a single piece of treasure."
    "Tenemos una pequeña pila de fichas cerca de nosotros, cada una representa una sola pieza del tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s26c_9ac5a7f3:

    # Marina "How does this game work?"
    Marina "Какие у этой игры правила?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s26c_28dc305b:

    # Amber "Basically, you try to get the cards in your hand to add up to 21, or as close as possible without going over."
    Amber "В общем, ты пытаешься сделать так, чтобы сумма карт в твоей руке стала равна 21, или ближайшей к этому числу, без превышения."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:499
translate spanish hwb_s26c_003cc9eb:

    # Amber "Whoever’s closest wins that round. The dealer can win too."
    Amber "Тот, кто ближе, выигрывает раунд. Дилер тоже может выиграть."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s26c_07de6ff1:

    # Amber "We all get two cards. Then, you can stand, which is where you don’t take any more cards, or you can hit, which is where you draw another."
    Amber "Вначале мы все получаем по две карты. Затем ты можешь спасовать и не брать больше карт, или взять еще."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:503
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a89cca99:

    # Marina "That sounds really easy."
    Marina "Звучит очень просто."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s26c_153089ed:

    # Amber "I guess. Like I said, it’s mostly luck."
    Amber "Так и есть. Как я и говорила, в основном дело в удаче."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s26c_20f15b71:

    # Mariah "Shut up. Time to play."
    Mariah "Заткнись. Пора играть."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s26c_fac59230:

    # "I flip her off but don’t argue."
    "Le hago un gesto obsceno, pero no discuto."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:546
translate spanish hwb_s26c_0986ed0d:

    # "Tess deals us the first hand. I stand while Mariah hits. I don’t expect her to beat my 18, but she lays down a ten, a three and a six."
    "Tess nos reparte la primera mano. Yo me planto mientras Mariah pide carta. No espero que supere mi 18, pero coloca un diez, un tres y un seis."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:550
translate spanish hwb_s26c_beef944e:

    # Amber "Damn."
    Amber "Черт."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s26c_3d99c0d6:

    # "Tess slides her two tokens."
    "Tess desliza sus dos fichas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:595
translate spanish hwb_s26c_4d29446f:

    # "On the next round, I beat her."
    "En la siguiente ronda, la venzo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:604
translate spanish hwb_s26c_35dc4632:

    # "I win the next two rounds after that, but then the dealer wins and we have to start over."
    "Gano las dos rondas siguientes, pero luego la crupier gana y tenemos que empezar de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:614
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e4da4c0c:

    # "The game drags on for a long time. Joseph has fallen asleep, head lolling backwards over the couch."
    "El juego se alarga por mucho tiempo. Joseph se ha quedado dormido, con la cabeza colgando hacia atrás sobre el sofá."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:616
translate spanish hwb_s26c_5be4bbd2:

    # "Even Marina, who has both her honor and money at stake here, is starting to fidget."
    "Incluso Marina, que tiene en juego tanto su honor como su dinero, empieza a inquietarse."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:618
translate spanish hwb_s26c_61d60da5:

    # "We’ve been playing for close to an hour. She doesn’t complain at all, though."
    "Llevamos casi una hora jugando. Sin embargo, ella no se queja en absoluto."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:620
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e9497b88:

    # "After a while, even Mariah and I are starting to get annoyed. She sighs and shifts irritatedly while I debate what to do."
    "Después de un rato, hasta Mariah y yo empezamos a molestarnos. Ella suspira y se mueve irritada mientras yo delibero qué hacer."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7abe0484:

    # "And when she takes her time thinking, I bite down the urge to say something snarky and hurry her along."
    "Y cuando se toma su tiempo para pensar, contengo las ganas de decir algo sarcástico para apurarla."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:624
translate spanish hwb_s26c_61a8f2d2:

    # "Once Tess wins again and we’re both sitting at three pieces each, Mariah wipes her palms and clears her throat."
    "Una vez que Tess gana de nuevo y ambas tenemos tres fichas cada una, Mariah se limpia las palmas y se aclara la garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:628
translate spanish hwb_s26c_dd0edd4d:

    # Mariah "This is taking forever."
    Mariah "Это длится уже вечность."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:632
translate spanish hwb_s26c_70900ede:

    # Amber "Yep."
    Amber "Угу."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s26c_fef14fea:

    # Amber "But if you’re saying we just call it here, the answer is no."
    Amber "Но если ты думаешь, что мы закончим на этом, то мой ответ — нет."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:636
translate spanish hwb_s26c_4490d665:

    # Mariah "No."
    Mariah "Нет."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:640
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ad91b8e3:

    # Mariah "But let’s just go all or nothing. One final hand."
    Mariah "Но давай просто пойдем ва-банк. Одну последнюю руку."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8b108b3a:

    # Mariah "Then you won’t be able to say I cheated, or took advantage of anyone, and I can finally relax with my treasure."
    Mariah "Тогда ты не сможешь сказать, что я сжульничала, или подговорила кого-нибудь, и я наконец смогу расслабиться с моим сокровищем."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:644
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ea94568b:

    # "I think about it. One more hand, huh? The odds are probably better than if we were to sit here all night."
    "Lo pienso. ¿Una mano más, eh? Las probabilidades probablemente sean mejores que si nos quedáramos aquí toda la noche."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e20006df:

    # "Maybe. I’m not good enough at math to calculate."
    "Tal vez. No soy lo suficientemente buena en matemáticas para calcularlo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:648
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a917b8c2:

    # "It would be possible that we’re here until the festival comes around, if we kept going back and forth like this."
    "Sería posible que estuviéramos aquí hasta que llegue el festival, si seguimos yendo y viniendo así."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d92d9378:

    # "I look over at Marina, whose interest has been piqued again."
    "Miro a Marina, cuyo interés se ha reavivado."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:654
translate spanish hwb_s26c_30cce854:

    # Amber "What do you think?"
    Amber "Что думаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:656
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7f6abbfb:

    # "She gives it a long thought, her face betraying nothing."
    "Lo piensa largamente, su rostro no traiciona nada."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:662
translate spanish hwb_s26c_f55ffc71:

    # "Then she shrugs."
    "Luego se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:664
translate spanish hwb_s26c_96b6ecfc:

    # Marina "I have no idea."
    Marina "Я понятия не имею."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7e146672:

    # "Right then."
    "Entonces, de acuerdo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:670
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ab6a35f7:

    # Amber "Fine. All or nothing."
    Amber "Хорошо. Все, или ничего."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:672
translate spanish hwb_s26c_4ad5e224:

    # "Mariah nods, satisfied."
    "Mariah asiente, satisfecha."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:676
translate spanish hwb_s26c_dfc66d09:

    # Mariah "Deal ‘em, kid."
    Mariah "Раздавай, мелкая."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:678
translate spanish hwb_s26c_fa57da0a:

    # "Tess passes out our cards."
    "Tess reparte nuestras cartas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:706
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8a645cb2:

    # "I pick mine up, holding them so only Marina can see."
    "Recojo las mías, sosteniéndolas para que solo Marina pueda verlas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s26c_635d93a3:

    # "A nine and a seven. Not awful, but not great."
    "Un nueve y un siete. No está mal, pero no es genial."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:724
translate spanish hwb_s26c_b6ce29eb:

    # "Tess is showing an eight."
    "Tess muestra un ocho."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s26c_19920a56:

    # "I try to gauge some sort of reaction from Mariah, but her face is totally expressionless. No wonder she beat Marina at poker."
    "Intento percibir algún tipo de reacción de Mariah, pero su cara está totalmente inexpresiva. No es de extrañar que le haya ganado a Marina al póker."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:730
translate spanish hwb_s26c_0a564cfa:

    # Tess "Amber?"
    Tess "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:732
translate spanish hwb_s26c_892f433d:

    # "I think that’s the first time she’s ever said my name. It sounds weird coming from her."
    "Creo que es la primera vez que dice mi nombre. Suena raro viniendo de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:736
translate spanish hwb_s26c_087777f7:

    # Amber "I’ll stand."
    Amber "Я пас."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:738
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d131445f:

    # "If I were to take a hit and draw another card, there’s a pretty good chance it’d put me over blackjack. And that would be a loss by default."
    "Si pidiera otra carta, hay una buena probabilidad de que me pase de veintiuno. Y eso sería una pérdida automática."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:742
translate spanish hwb_s26c_31d7953a:

    # Tess "Sis?"
    Tess "Сеструх?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:744
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7a9bf03c:

    # Mariah "Hit me."
    Mariah "Дай мне."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:758
translate spanish hwb_s26c_544e7033:

    # "Tess slides her another card, then flips one over the hole card."
    "Tess le desliza otra carta, luego voltea una sobre la carta tapada."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:760
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d0270e6d:

    # "It’s a four, for a grand total of 12. That means we still beat her, at least."
    "Es un cuatro, para un total de 12. Eso significa que al menos aún le ganamos."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:764
translate spanish hwb_s26c_117818b1:

    # Tess "Let’s see."
    Tess "Вскрываемся."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:766
translate spanish hwb_s26c_be2dbb42:

    # "I lay down my cards, and wait for Mariah to do the same."
    "Pongo mis cartas sobre la mesa y espero a que Mariah haga lo mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:768
translate spanish hwb_s26c_89ce464a:

    # "Except she doesn’t."
    "Excepto que no lo hace."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:770
translate spanish hwb_s26c_f224a578:

    # "She just looks at my cards, flat on the table. Face stony, mouth silent."
    "Solo mira mis cartas, extendidas sobre la mesa. Con el rostro pétreo, la boca en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:776
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c41c5f2d:

    # "Then she makes a sound of disgust and stands as she flings her three cards towards the table. I flip them over to see a three, a two, and a ten."
    "Luego emite un sonido de disgusto y se levanta mientras lanza sus tres cartas hacia la mesa. Las volteo para ver un tres, un dos y un diez."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:782
translate spanish hwb_s26c_26a8f921:

    # Amber "We win."
    Amber "Мы выиграли."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:784
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ea757b5b:

    # "That’s all I say."
    "Eso es todo lo que digo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:786
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c72fc820:

    # "Marina looks at me, then at the table, then back to me. Making sure she heard me right."
    "Marina me mira, luego a la mesa, y luego de vuelta a mí. Asegurándose de haber escuchado bien."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:790
translate spanish hwb_s26c_511ed752:

    # Marina "We did?"
    Marina "Мы выиграли?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:792
translate spanish hwb_s26c_6385fc43:

    # Amber "Yeah. The total of our hand was closer to 21 than hers was."
    Amber "Ага. Сумма в нашей руке была ближе к 21, чем у нее."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:794
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8fd93238:

    # "Strangely, I don’t even feel excited. Not about the victory, which is nice, or the fact that it came over Mariah, which is nicer. I just feel relieved."
    "Extrañamente, ni siquiera me siento emocionada. No por la victoria, que está bien, ni por el hecho de que fue contra Mariah, que es mejor. Solo siento alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:798
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8ec6a9d7:

    # "Marina squeals and then explodes towards, half leaping, half tackling me into a hug as I nearly fall off the couch. She plants a large kiss on my cheek, and then travels over to my mouth."
    "Marina chilla y luego se lanza hacia mí, medio saltando, medio tackleándome en un abrazo mientras casi me caigo del sofá. Me planta un gran beso en la mejilla, y luego se desplaza hacia mi boca."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:800
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a698951d:

    # Marina "Oh God, Amber! I was so worried but oh my God! Thank you! You’re the best!"
    Marina "О боже, Эмбер! Я так волновалась, но господи! Спасибо тебе! Ты самая лучшая!"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:802
translate spanish hwb_s26c_dc64f285:

    # "Her praises are dotted with kisses all over my face."
    "Sus elogios están salpicados de besos por toda mi cara."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:808
translate spanish hwb_s26c_38c0082e:

    # "Joseph, woken up by the commotion, looks away with a blush. Tess, on the other hand, stares at us, creepily apathetic."
    "Joseph, despertado por el alboroto, desvía la mirada sonrojado. Tess, por otro lado, nos mira con una apatía escalofriante."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:813
translate spanish hwb_s26c_b59dd749:

    # "I separate myself from Marina and stand up. Mariah has already traveled halfway to the door, not saying anything in her defeat."
    "Me separo de Marina y me levanto. Mariah ya ha recorrido la mitad del camino hacia la puerta, sin decir nada en su derrota."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:815
translate spanish hwb_s26c_17e7c4ac:

    # "The little wooden box of gold sits abandoned where her arm was. I check and count the pieces of treasure. They’re all there."
    "La pequeña caja de madera con oro yace abandonada donde estaba su brazo. Reviso y cuento las piezas del tesoro. Están todas ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:817
translate spanish hwb_s26c_affaf52d:

    # "I start to move towards Mariah, to say something, but Joseph clucks his tongue. I stop."
    "Empiezo a moverme hacia Mariah para decir algo, pero Joseph chasquea la lengua. Me detengo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:821
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a4c5a642:

    # Joseph "Don’t worry about her. She’s always like this."
    Joseph "Не волнуйся об этом. Она всегда так."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:825
translate spanish hwb_s26c_927286b4:

    # Amber "Sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:827
translate spanish hwb_s26c_5c8b3ee9:

    # "Not sure what else to say, I half-shrug. Which is hard, since Marina still clings to my arm."
    "Sin saber qué más decir, me encojo de hombros a medias. Lo cual es difícil, ya que Marina sigue aferrada a mi brazo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:832
translate spanish hwb_s26c_222dfaae:

    # Joseph "Don’t be. Better things work out this way."
    Joseph "Не извиняйся. Так будет лучше."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:834
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7a9e5863:

    # Joseph "C’mon, kiddo."
    Joseph "Пойдем, мелкая."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:842
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e0a82710:

    # "He takes Tess’ hand and they start to follow Mariah, who’s left the building."
    "Toma la mano de Tess y comienzan a seguir a Mariah, que ya ha salido del edificio."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:844
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8daf185f:

    # Joseph "You ladies take care."
    Joseph "Вы берегите себя, дамочки."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:846
translate spanish hwb_s26c_913e165c:

    # Amber "You too."
    Amber "И вы себя тоже."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:850
translate spanish hwb_s26c_baeb3dbd:

    # Marina "See you later!"
    Marina "Увидимся!"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:857
translate spanish hwb_s26c_aa8765a1:

    # "Once they leave, I look down at the mess of chips and cards on the table. Someone will come by and clean them up."
    "Una vez que se van, miro el desorden de fichas y cartas sobre la mesa. Alguien vendrá a limpiarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:864
translate spanish hwb_s26c_84032a0c:

    # "Marina tugs on my shirt. When I look at her, she kisses me on the lips again."
    "Marina tira de mi camisa. Cuando la miro, me besa en los labios otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:866
translate spanish hwb_s26c_94b23ce0:

    # "For the first time today, we stay like that for a long time. Not caring about how many stares we might be getting. Though it can’t be more than three."
    "Por primera vez hoy, nos quedamos así por un largo rato. Sin importarnos cuántas miradas podamos estar recibiendo. Aunque no pueden ser más de tres."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:868
translate spanish hwb_s26c_817d67e8:

    # "I can still taste a faint saltiness from her tears."
    "Todavía puedo sentir un leve sabor salado de sus lágrimas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:870
translate spanish hwb_s26c_b804b8b1:

    # "I feel her lips curve into a smile even before we pull apart."
    "Siento que sus labios se curvan en una sonrisa incluso antes de separarnos."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:872
translate spanish hwb_s26c_455084ce:

    # Marina "Thank you. Seriously."
    Marina "Спасибо тебе. Огромное."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:874
translate spanish hwb_s26c_a4ed1a39:

    # Marina "I know I’m always saying ‘thank you’ and ‘sorry.’ But I am sorry that I screw up so much."
    Marina "Я знаю, я постоянно говорю “спасибо” и “прости”, но... Прости меня, за то что все так порчу."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:876
translate spanish hwb_s26c_5df7e882:

    # Amber "Don’t worry about it. It all worked out, right?"
    Amber "Забудь об этом. Все ведь сложилось хорошо, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:880
translate spanish hwb_s26c_de8f5551:

    # Marina "Yeah. But only because you were there."
    Marina "Да. Но только потому, что ты была рядом."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:882
translate spanish hwb_s26c_8c9ddc1f:

    # Marina "I dunno what I would’ve done if you weren’t."
    Marina "Я не знаю, что бы я делала, если бы тебя не было."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:884
translate spanish hwb_s26c_ff169c7d:

    # Amber "Well if I wasn’t then you wouldn’t be either, you know?"
    Amber "Ну, если бы меня не было, то и тебя бы тут не было, так ведь?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:886
translate spanish hwb_s26c_946ce263:

    # "I mean it as a joke, but she doesn’t laugh. Just leans into me."
    "Lo digo en broma, pero ella no se ríe. Solo se recuesta contra mí."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:888
translate spanish hwb_s26c_69522317:

    # Marina "I know."
    Marina "Я знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:890
translate spanish hwb_s26c_99a34d86:

    # "Then we kiss again."
    "Entonces nos besamos otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:892
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7b2b19e0:

    # "We must look like perverts, just standing in the middle of a casino making out."
    "Debemos parecer unas pervertidas, solo paradas en medio de un casino besándonos."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:896
translate spanish hwb_s26c_09e5f4cb:

    # Amber "You ready to get out of Vegas?"
    Amber "Готова сбежать из Вегаса?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:900
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d8fc18d7:

    # Marina "Definitely. But um, one thing first."
    Marina "Определенно. Но перед этим еще кое-что."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:902
translate spanish hwb_s26c_07534e69:

    # Amber "What’s that?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:904
translate spanish hwb_s26c_0a47f458:

    # Marina "Can we get something to eat?"
    Marina "Давай мы что-нибудь поедим?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:908
translate spanish hwb_s26c_7721cb3b:

    # Amber "I was hoping you’d say that. I saw this Chinese place earlier that smelled amazing. Sound good?"
    Amber "Я надеялась, что ты это скажешь. Видела какой-то китайский ресторанчик неподалеку, там такой запах... Как тебе?"

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:912
translate spanish hwb_s26c_01365fc5:

    # Marina "Very."
    Marina "Чудесно."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:956
translate spanish hwb_s26c_221f50ca:

    # "Hand in hand like always, we leave the casino and make the quick walk to the restaurant. I’d come across it while waiting for Marina before."
    "Tomadas de la mano como siempre, salimos del casino y caminamos rápido al restaurante. Lo había encontrado antes mientras esperaba a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:958
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e96f4ba9:

    # "All along the Strip, more and more lights are coming on."
    "A lo largo del Strip, cada vez más luces se encienden."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:960
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e5b41f2d:

    # "It’s hard to tell that it’s getting much darker out, because of how much artificial light there is."
    "Es difícil notar que está oscureciendo más, por toda la luz artificial que hay."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:962
translate spanish hwb_s26c_e53d67fe:

    # "We get to the restaurant and eat outside on the patio, watching as more and more buildings are illuminated."
    "Llegamos al restaurante y cenamos afuera en la terraza, viendo cómo más y más edificios se iluminan."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:964
translate spanish hwb_s26c_828bf6bf:

    # "By the time we’re done and back at the RV, Las Vegas has shifted fully from daytime to artificial-daytime."
    "Para cuando terminamos y volvemos a la casa rodante, Las Vegas ha pasado por completo del día al día artificial."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:966
translate spanish hwb_s26c_d40f1cc0:

    # "Before we buckle in, I pull back all of the curtains."
    "Antes de abrocharnos el cinturón, corro todas las cortinas."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:968
translate spanish hwb_s26c_2d3dd8d5:

    # Amber "Make sure you get a good spot by the window."
    Amber "Садись у окошка."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:970
translate spanish hwb_s26c_122d5cfb:

    # Amber "You’re gonna wanna see this."
    Amber "Тебе стоит на это взглянуть."

# game/script/hwb_s26c.rpy:798
translate spanish hwb_s26c_c88ecca1:

    # "Marina squeals and then explodes towards me, half leaping, half tackling me into a hug as I nearly fall off the couch. She plants a large kiss on my cheek, and then travels over to my mouth."
    "Marina chilla y luego se lanza hacia mí, medio saltando, medio embistiéndome en un abrazo mientras casi me caigo del sofá. Me planta un gran beso en la mejilla, y luego se desplaza hacia mi boca."

